# Divyah Infotech - Netlify Redirects Configuration

# Force HTTPS (handled automatically by Netlify, but explicit here)
http://divyahinfotech.com/*    https://divyahinfotech.com/:splat    301!
http://www.divyahinfotech.com/*    https://www.divyahinfotech.com/:splat    301!

# Redirect www to non-www (RECOMMENDED for cleaner URLs)
https://www.divyahinfotech.com/*    https://divyahinfotech.com/:splat    301!

# Alternative: Redirect non-www to www (uncomment if preferred)
# https://divyahinfotech.com/*    https://www.divyahinfotech.com/:splat    301!

# 404 fallback - redirect all 404s to homepage
/*    /index.html    404
